{"lemma":"حَلَقَ","slug":"حَلَقَ","root":"ح.ل.ق","root_slug":"ح-ل-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ل-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":7,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":23},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8865","n8869","n8870","n8871","n8872"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to shave, to shear"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to peel"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to destroy"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut off entirely"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause pain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to injure in the throat","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill (a cistern)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to determine approximately"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to shave smooth"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to soar into the air, to fly in circles"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rise"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have a halo"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be three-quarters ripe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make round"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to surround"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to clothe"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَلَقَ (ḥalaqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"shaving"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"throat"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"back of the throat, pharynx"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chasm"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rings","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pair of earrings","tags":["Egypt"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8865","headword_ar":"حلّق","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoliyqN","text_ar":"تَحْلِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, first sentence.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~qhu HaloqapF","text_ar":"حلّقهُ حَلْقَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He clad him with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqp","text_ar":"حلقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coat of mail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~Nq HaloqapF","text_ar":"حلٌّق حَلْقَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He turned"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a circle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence, perhaps,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q EalaY A@somi fulaAnK","text_ar":"حلّق عَلَى ا@سْمِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[if, as I suppose, originally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew a line round the name of such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cancelled the stipend,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"allowance, of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q AlA_ibila","text_ar":"حلّق الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He branded the camels with a mark in the form of a ring:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see the pass. part. n.] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlaq biA_iSobEihi","text_ar":"حلَق بِاـِصْبعِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bent his finger round like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqap","text_ar":"حَلْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q","text_ar":"حلّق"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of the moon,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It had a halo around it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHl~q","text_ar":"تحلّق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b7-  Said of a bird, inf. n. as above, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It soared in its flight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and circled in the air."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-  Said of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najom","text_ar":"نَجْم"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) meaning the Pleiades ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~uray~aA","text_ar":"الثُّرَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fgr","text_ar":"فغر"},{"kind":"text","text":",) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, high:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became overhead."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T ubi suprà: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fagara","text_ar":"فَغَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) It is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoliyqu Al$~amosi","text_ar":"تَحْلِيقُ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the former part of the day, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun's rising high from the east:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in the latter part of the day,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sun's going down:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but Sh says, I know not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AltHlyq","text_ar":"التحليق"},{"kind":"text","text":"except as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the being,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming, high."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q","text_ar":"حلّق"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bibaSarihi A_ilaY Als~amA='i","text_ar":"بِبَصَرِهِ اـِلَى السَّما=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his eyes towards the sky."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q DaroEu Aln~aAqapi","text_ar":"حلّق ضَرْعُ النَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel's milk became drawn up"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and consequently"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her udder"},{"kind":"text","text":"also] (IDrd, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to her belly"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, TA.) And accord. to ISd,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q","text_ar":"حلّق"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~abanu","text_ar":"اللَّبَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became drawn up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withdrawn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q","text_ar":"حلّق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of the water in a drinking-trough, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became little in quantity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hal~aqato Euyuwnu AlA_ibili","text_ar":"حَلَّقَتْ عُيُونُ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eyes of the camels sank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became depressed, in their heads."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, K, TA.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q Albusoru","text_ar":"حلّق البُسْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ripening dates became ripe"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as far as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloq","text_ar":"حَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the extent of two thirds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqana","text_ar":"حَلْقَنَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they began to be ripe"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqn","text_ar":"حلقن"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next the base;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in that art.;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqama","text_ar":"حَلْقَمَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqm","text_ar":"حلقم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q bihi","text_ar":"حلّق بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a draught of [milk and water such as is termed]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuwaAH","text_ar":"صُوَاح"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused his belly to become inflated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-' Abbád, K, TA.) ―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl~q biAl$~aYo'a A_ilayohi","text_ar":"حلّق بِالشَّىْءَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw the thing to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","IDrd","AHn"]},{"entry_id":"n8869","headword_ar":"حَلْقٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence, by a synecdoche, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gullet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"œsophagus:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galoSamap","text_ar":"غَلْصَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"epiglottis"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of slaughter in an animal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part of the neck:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj in his “ Khalk el-Insán: ”) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passage of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place by which pass, the food and drink, into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariYo'","text_ar":"مَرِىْء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"œsophagus"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuloquwmN","text_ar":"حُلْقُومٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) [but] the latter is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"windpipe;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passage of the breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj ubi suprà, Az, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which has branches branching from it into the lungs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[namely,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bronchi, consisting of two main branches, which divide into smaller and smaller,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSab","text_ar":"قَصَب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj ubi suprà, and Msb:) [this word ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqwm","text_ar":"حلقوم"},{"kind":"text","text":"), however, as well as the former, is sometimes applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gullet:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but the former ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlq","text_ar":"حلق"},{"kind":"text","text":") generally signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the latter ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqwm","text_ar":"حلقوم"},{"kind":"text","text":"), the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"windpipe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see another explanation of the latter word in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqm","text_ar":"حلقم"},{"kind":"text","text":", from the M:) a morsel of food, or the like, is commonly said to stick in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlq","text_ar":"حلق"},{"kind":"text","text":", but not in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hlqwm","text_ar":"حلقوم"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqN","text_ar":"حَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the masc. gender: (Msb:) and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuluwqN","text_ar":"حُلُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) and sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuluqN","text_ar":"حُلُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HilaqN","text_ar":"حِلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is extr.; and pl. of pauc."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHolaAqN","text_ar":"اَحْلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoluqN","text_ar":"اَحْلُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is allowable [as a pl. of pauc.] on the ground of analogy; but it has not been heard from the Arabs: (Msb:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuloquwmN","text_ar":"حُلْقُومٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEoluwmN","text_ar":"فُعْلُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"being augmentative, (Msb,) accord. to Kh; but of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEoluwlN","text_ar":"فُعْلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to others: (TA:) and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaAqiymu","text_ar":"حَلَاقِيمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and, by contraction,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaAqimu","text_ar":"حَلَاقِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The part through which the water runs"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a watering-trough or tank, and of a vessel: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuluwqN","text_ar":"حُلُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuluwqN","text_ar":"حُلُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water-courses,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"valleys,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a land; and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strait, places,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a land, (K, TA,) and of roads. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqu Aljaw~i","text_ar":"حَلْقُ الجَوِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The upper region of the air:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 2, as said of a bird, &c.]. (Z, TA.) ―         -b5-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloq","text_ar":"حَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a date is (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part at the extremity of two thirds"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a part near to the base"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unluckiness"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to others"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, K.) Hence, [accord. to some,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqorFA HaloqFA","text_ar":"عَقْرًا حَلْقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[explained above: see 1]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","TA","S","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n8870","headword_ar":"حُلْقٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of being bereft of a child by death;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vukolN","text_ar":"ثُكْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ukol","text_ar":"شُكْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) So in the prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^um~ika AlHuloqu","text_ar":"لِاُمِّكَ الحُلْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May bereavement of her child befall thy mother"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, accord. to the A, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shaving of the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"[on account of such, or a similar, bereavement]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8871","headword_ar":"حِلْقٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Numerous cattle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) because the herbage is cropped by them like as hair is shaven or shorn. (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a fulaAnN biAlHiloqi","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ فُلَانٌ بِالحِلْقِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlA_iHoraAfi","text_ar":"وَالاـِحْرَافِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one came with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought, much cattle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrf","text_ar":"حرف"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sealring"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is on the hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"finger"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a king:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a seal-ring of silver, without a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faS~","text_ar":"فَصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gem set in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISd, K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uEoTiYa fulaAnN","text_ar":"اُعْطِىَ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHiloqa","text_ar":"الحِلْقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was made prince,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"governor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commander."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","IAar","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n8872","headword_ar":"حَلَقٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also Camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branded with the mark termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqapN","text_ar":"حَلْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHal~aqapN","text_ar":"مُحَلَّقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}